{
  "stem": "1873.4",
  "chunk_idx": 12,
  "model": "openai/gpt-oss-120b",
  "elapsed_s": 8.6,
  "sentences_input": [
    {
      "segment_idx": 48,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 5,
      "text": "Much less, because about 30 people were involved in the organization.",
      "word_count": 11
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 49,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 0,
      "text": "And this maybe is the reason for the success.",
      "word_count": 9
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 49,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 1,
      "text": "And maybe still, we wouldn't escape.",
      "word_count": 6
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 49,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 2,
      "text": "The leader of the underground organization was Leon Feldhendler from a city [?",
      "word_count": 13
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 49,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 3,
      "text": "Zulkeflee ?] in Poland.",
      "word_count": 4
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 49,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 4,
      "text": "Maybe still we would, at the end, we'll be able to talk about the revolt and we would be killed anyway.",
      "word_count": 21
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 49,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 5,
      "text": "But in 1943, in the end, the Germans were liquidating the ghettos in the east because the Red Army was pushing.",
      "word_count": 21
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 49,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 6,
      "text": "At that time, they liquidated a ghetto of Minsk, and they brought the Minsk Jews to Sobibor.",
      "word_count": 17
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 49,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 7,
      "text": "Now, when a transport of Minsk Jews arrived, there were so many people that the Nazis didn't have enough-- they picked up some people to help us.",
      "word_count": 27
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 49,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 8,
      "text": "And they were looking for young people.",
      "word_count": 7
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 49,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 9,
      "text": "They picked up about 70 young people, not realizing that most of them are former Russian POWs.",
      "word_count": 17
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 49,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 10,
      "text": "You see, when the Nazis discovered a Jew as a prisoner-- in a prisoner of war camps, they immediately took him out.",
      "word_count": 22
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 49,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 11,
      "text": "So they took them out and put them in the, in the Minsk ghetto.",
      "word_count": 14
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 49,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 12,
      "text": "And when the Minsk ghetto was liquidated, they brought them to Sobibor.",
      "word_count": 12
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 49,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 13,
      "text": "And when in Sobibor, young people were selected.",
      "word_count": 8
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 49,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 14,
      "text": "This Frenzel picked up the young people, and he picked up quite a few former officers from the Soviet Army.",
      "word_count": 20
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 49,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 15,
      "text": "And Feldhendler immediately recognized the possibilities.",
      "word_count": 6
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 49,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 16,
      "text": "And we get-- there was a man called Sasha Peshkosky.",
      "word_count": 10
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 49,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 17,
      "text": "He was a lieutenant in the Soviet Army, who did look very healthy.",
      "word_count": 13
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 49,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 18,
      "text": "There was something in him, and he was big [INAUDIBLE].",
      "word_count": 10
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 49,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 19,
      "text": "He had contact with them.",
      "word_count": 5
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 49,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 20,
      "text": "And finally because of him, because of his knowledge, the organization took off.",
      "word_count": 13
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 49,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 21,
      "text": "And we decided to escape October 13, 1943.",
      "word_count": 8
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 49,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 22,
      "text": "The plan was very simple.",
      "word_count": 5
    }
  ],
